            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">12.204</ph> Solicitation/contract form.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d684e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d698e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall use the <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/solicitationcontractorder-commercial-items"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">Standard Form 1449</xref>, Solicitation/Contract/Order for Commercial Items, if (1) the acquisition is expected to exceed the simplified acquisition threshold; (2) a paper solicitation or contract is being issued; and (3) procedures at <xref href="FAR-i1112649.dita#i1112649"
                        base="i1112649"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">12.603</xref> are not being used. Use of the <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/solicitationcontractorder-commercial-items"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">SF 1449</xref> is nonmandatory but encouraged for commercial acquisitions not exceeding the simplified acquisition threshold.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d698e35" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Consistent with the requirements at <xref href="FAR-i1120755.dita#i1120755"
                        base="i1120755"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">5.203</xref>(a) and (h), the contracting officer may allow fewer than 15 days before issuance of the solicitation.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
